OL,6,GA couple of relatively insignificant
OL,7,Gblips on BBC News from earlier today.
OL,9,FThis morning, the intermittent issue
OL,10,Fwith the augmented reality newsroom
OL,11,F"hoop" reared its head again.
OL,13,FDuring the opening sequence for the
OL,14,F10am news programme, the AR hoop was
OL,15,Fseen hovering underneath the real hoop.
OL,17,FThe AR version has been in use for many
OL,18,Fmonths now. It's intended to cover up
OL,19,Fthe real newsroom hoop, which developed
OL,20,Fa fault last year, leaving a portion of
OL,21,Fthe display blank.
OL,3,CA couple of minor glitches on BBC News
OL,4,Ctoday
